{"tid":2443675,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［西灣河槍擊同的士撞人案］ 律政司指許智峯潛逃要求私人檢控撤案","createTime":"2021-03-12T07:55:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T15:04:14.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"294e1c5f84161464f9d2aa18229df87900082e69","tid":2443675,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:55:14.000Z","msg":"現流亡海外的前立法會議員許智峯，早前就律政司介入前年西灣河警員開槍案、及深水埗的士司機撞人案申請司法覆核，要求推翻律政司司長撤銷檢控的決定，今（12 日）於高等法院進行聆訊，爭議許智峯是否適合作出司法覆核。律政司質疑許智峯棄保潛逃，應拒絕其司法覆核申請。法官李運騰聽畢雙方陳詞，訂於 5 月 14 日或之前，就本爭議頒下書面判詞，再排期處理司法覆核。<br />\n<br />\n許智峯昨日在 Facebook 提及本案，指在如此墮落的司法系統下，已經不會有僥倖心態覺得會贏官司。「但就算最後輸了，我希望讓熊仔餅及被的士撞的手足知道，香港人沒有放棄過，起碼我們有盡力嘗試到最後」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/許智峯就-2-私人檢控被撤提覆核-律政司指許潛逃要求撤案/?fbclid=IwAR3QUf-Rs-hiesk5z2_lhKCUlQzp9-RsgTGlTuNwo1hpb4UBVFTEzMsUoxw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%AF%E5%B0%B1-2-%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E8%A2%AB%E6%92%A4%E6%8F%90%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8-%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E6%8C%87%E8%A8%B1%E6%BD%9B%E9%80%83%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%92%A4%E6%A1%88%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3QUf-Rs-hiesk5z2_lhKCUlQzp9-RsgTGlTuNwo1hpb4UBVFTEzMsUoxw&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw30iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=fc70f80d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%AF%E5%B0%B1-2-%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E8%A2%AB%E6%92%A4%E6%8F%90%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8-%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E6%8C%87%E8%A8%B1%E6%BD%9B%E9%80%83%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%92%A4%E6%A1%88%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3QUf-Rs-hiesk5z2_lhKCUlQzp9-RsgTGlTuNwo1hpb4UBVFTEzMsUoxw&h=b6da3dc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/許智峯就-2-私人檢控被撤提覆核-律政司指許潛逃要求撤案/?fbclid=IwAR3QUf-Rs-hiesk5z2_lhKCUlQzp9-RsgTGlTuNwo1hpb4UBVFTEzMsUoxw</a>"},{"pid":"e4a4ad7396be5cb4673742ecea771c63811bed5c","tid":2443675,"uid":144919,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"294e1c5f84161464f9d2aa182